        "People have different views about families that fly overseas to find a better jobs. While others believe it will make their kids struggle, I believe that it will be beneficial for the family's offspring.",
        "As families move abroad their kids are welcome to a better education prospects. It will help them to pursue their learning in a well-known school or university which can allow them to have better education. Furthermore they can have better knowledge and be armed with skills that are needed in life.",
